#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/intro/upgrade-from-v1.md ../src/guide/intro/upgrade-from-v2.md
msgid "Typical mappings to consider are:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/intro/upgrade-from-v1.md
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"| Yii 1.1 | Yii3 |\n"
"|---------|------|\n"
"| `protected/controllers` | `src/Web/*/Action.php` or controller-like services |\n"
"| `protected/models` | `src/Domain`, `src/Shared`, `src/Db`, or form models by responsibility |\n"
"| `protected/views` | templates near the feature, for example `src/Web/HomePage/template.php` |\n"
"| `protected/views/layouts` | layout templates and assets under `src/Web/Shared/Layout` |\n"
"| `protected/components` | services configured in the dependency injection container |\n"
"| `protected/extensions` | Composer packages or local packages |\n"
"| `protected/commands` | `src/Console/*Command.php` |\n"
"| `protected/messages` | translator message files |\n"
"| `protected/config` | `config/common`, `config/web`, `config/console`, `config/environments` |\n"
"| `webroot` | `public` |\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/intro/upgrade-from-v1.md
msgid "Do not recreate `protected` in Yii3. Put PHP source under `src`, public files under `public`, generated/runtime files under `runtime`, and configuration under `config`."
msgstr ""

