#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/intro/upgrade-from-v1.md
msgid "These Yii 1.1 refactorings make the old behavior easier to understand and reuse:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: ../src/guide/intro/upgrade-from-v1.md
msgid "isolate database queries from controllers;"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: ../src/guide/intro/upgrade-from-v1.md
msgid "remove direct `Yii::app()` access from domain code;"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: ../src/guide/intro/upgrade-from-v1.md
msgid "move validation out of Active Record when it describes request input rather than database invariants;"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: ../src/guide/intro/upgrade-from-v1.md
msgid "replace large controller actions with services;"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: ../src/guide/intro/upgrade-from-v1.md
msgid "document all routes and URL rules;"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: ../src/guide/intro/upgrade-from-v1.md
msgid "add tests around the flows you plan to rebuild first;"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: ../src/guide/intro/upgrade-from-v1.md
msgid "upgrade PHP syntax gradually if the old runtime allows it."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/intro/upgrade-from-v1.md
msgid "The goal is not to make Yii 1.1 look like Yii3. The goal is to reduce hidden coupling before the code crosses the framework boundary."
msgstr ""
